data.description: You will love this one owner, well maintained, custom open floorplan in Greenwhich Park with 3 bedroom and  2 baths!  This is one of the largest main floor plans you will see in the development with a large open kitchen and spacious primary bedroom floorplan.  The primary bedroom boasts a large suite with a sitting area and access to an outside patio with retractable awning.  The primary bathroom is equipped with a soaker tub, double sinks, walk in shower and a custom built walk-in closet.  You will be amazed at the large eat in kitchen complete with plenty of cabinet storage and an island and dining area with access to a lovely screened in porch perfect to enjoy the cooler evenings! Single entry attached rear garage is oversized complete with shelving for your storage needs as well as a pull down attic access.  The HOA covers lawn mowing, snow removal and 1x a year window washing.  So many amenities to enjoy including easy access to Meritus Hospital, Black Rock Golf Course, Hagerstown Community College and minutes to I70 Interstate.  Schedule your tour today to see what Greenwich Park has to offer and buy with confidence complete with a one year home warranty!!!
